<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero">
        <div class="text-start py-0">
          <p class="accent-text" data-aos="fade-up">Hi, I am </p>
          <h1 data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" class="hero-title">Avis Ejerenwa</h1>
          <h1 data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" class="hero-subtitle">I love to build solutions for the web.</h1>
          <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300" class="hero-caption"> <span class="accent-text">I am, </span> a software
            engineer focused on developing modern web solutions and solving real-world problems with clean code.</p>
          <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-accent-transparent mt-3" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">View My Work</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section id="about" class="container py-5">
      <div class="row align-items-center">
        <!-- Left Column: Text Content -->
        <div class="col-lg-8 text-justify mb-4 pe-5">
          <h2 data-aos="fade-up"  class=" mb-4" ><span class="accent-text">01.</span> About Me</h2>
          <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100" class="mb-4">
            Hello! My name is <span class="fw-bold">Avis Ejerenwa</span>, and I enjoy creating and developing solutions,
            whether it’s improving real-life workflows or building utility applications that supercharge productivity.
            My journey in software development began in 2009, when I learned Core Java at <span class="accent">MIIT</span>
            to build a stock-keeping application for my dad's store, a project that sparked my passion for solving problems
            through technology.
          </p>
          <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="150" class="mb-4">
            Since then, I’ve had the privilege of working with <span class="accent">Triumph Courier Services</span>, a
            last-mile package delivery provider in Atlanta,
            where I developed a full-fledged Delivery Dashboard and other tools to streamline operations and boost
            efficiency. I also collaborated with
            <span class="accent">Paris Beauty and Hair Salon</span> to design and develop their website, featuring an
            integrated scheduler for managing appointments and payments.
          </p>
          <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" class="mb-4">
            Today, as an <span class="fw-bold">Experienced Software Engineer</span>, I specialize in building scalable,
            high-performance software systems and user-centric web applications.
            I have extensive experience in full stack development, Agile methodologies, and collaborating with
            cross-functional teams to deliver innovative solutions.
            My focus includes reducing technical debt, improving system performance, and staying at the forefront of
            emerging technologies.
          </p>
          <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="250">
            Here are a few technologies and tools I’ve been working with recently:
          </p>
          <!-- Technologies List -->
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-6">
              <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100" class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right accent"></i> Java, JavaScript</li>
                <li data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300" class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right accent"></i> HTML/CSS, Node.js</li>
                <li data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500" class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right accent"></i> MongoDB</li>
                <li data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="700" class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right accent"></i> Git, GitHub</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-6">
              <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right accent"></i> React, Bootstrap, Express.js</li>
                <li data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400" class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right accent"></i> REST APIs</li>
                <li data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600" class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right accent"></i> UI/UX Design (Figma, Adobe Suite)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    
        <!-- Right Column: Image -->
        <div class="col-lg-4 text-center d-flex align-items-start">
          <div class="position-relative w-100">
            <div class="image-container">
              <img
              src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AP1GczNTAC5slZlSOPomLNDR3x1j7mnkZ3YtIH-8JlnRLnp_07_eIc6LFoisSYZIYWmkL17U58X6xIVTu5j_g8h9M9T4inMbJ9HD57RPR7-W8hEZkWOCZHOcNSEiMGeIt5hWTe0j6BXojAFYhgHOs45kTIZteA=w684-h1049-s-no-gm?authuser=0"
              alt="Your Image" class="img-fluid rounded" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>


      </div>
